## âœï¸ Typing Logic

```jsx
if (!isDeleting) {
  setText(currentWord.substring(0, charIndex + 1));
  setCharIndex(charIndex + 1);
```

* Takes **1 more letter** each time
* Example:

  * `R`
  * `Re`
  * `Rea`

---

### â¸ Pause After Full Word

```jsx
if (charIndex === currentWord.length) {
  setTimeout(() => setIsDeleting(true), 1000);
}
```

* Waits **1 second**
* Then starts deleting

---

## âŒ Deleting Logic

```jsx
else {
  setText(currentWord.substring(0, charIndex - 1));
  setCharIndex(charIndex - 1);
```

* Removes letters one by one
* Example:

  * `React App`
  * `React Ap`
  * `React A`

---

### ğŸ” Move to Next Word

```jsx
if (charIndex === 0) {
  setIsDeleting(false);
  setWordIndex((wordIndex + 1) % words.length);
}
```

* When word is fully deleted:

  * Stop deleting
  * Go to next word
  * `% words.length` loops back to first word

---

### 8ï¸âƒ£ Cleanup (Important)

```jsx
